{"html": [{"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">ACUERDOS ADOPTADOS POR EL BANCO CENTRAL DE CHILE EN SU SESION N&#xBA; 393</div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Certifico que el Banco Central de Chile en su Sesi&#xF3;n N&#xBA; 393, celebrada el 7 de Diciembre de 1994, celebr&#xF3; los siguientes acuerdos:</div><br><div class=\"p\">393-03-941207 - Autoriza a Banco Santander - Chile para emitir tarjeta de cr&#xE9;dito &quot;JCPenney&quot;.</div><br></div>", "i": 6569375}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Se acord&#xF3; autorizar a Banco Santander - Chile para emitir la tarjeta de cr&#xE9;dito que se indica:</div><br><div class=\"p\">Entidad Emisora&nbsp; &nbsp; Tarjeta a emitir&nbsp; &nbsp;  Modalidad</div><br><div class=\"p\">Banco</div><div class=\"p\">Santander-Chile&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  JCPenney&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Para ser utilizada</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  en las compras que</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  se efect&#xFA;en en los</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  establecimientos</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  JCPenney en el</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  territorio de Chile,</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  y obtener avances en</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &n